<chapter>
	<title>XML Import/Export</title>
	<sect1>
		<title>Introduction</title>
		<simpara>Scarab allows module administrators to:</simpara>
		<itemizedlist>
			<listitem>
				<simpara>export</simpara>
				<itemizedlist>
					<listitem>
						<simpara>issues of a module (data);</simpara>
					</listitem>
					<listitem>
						<simpara>issue types and attributes of a module (metadata);</simpara>
					</listitem>
				</itemizedlist>
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
				<simpara>import</simpara>
				<itemizedlist>
					<listitem>
						<simpara>data to update or create issues in a module.</simpara>
					</listitem>
				</itemizedlist>
			</listitem>
		</itemizedlist>
		<simpara>In the current development of Scarab it is not possible (yet) to import the metadata, i.e. issue types and attributes.</simpara>
	</sect1>
